 filing as a per-client, per-tax-year engagement. Supports a five-state machine (START ‚Üí IN_PROCESSING ‚Üí PENDING_CLIENT_REVIEW ‚Üí SUBMIT_TO_CRA ‚Üí COMPLETED) with any-to-‚Ä¶","sessionId":"10e14017-2f3e-4428-9177-17ccd5eb1fb1","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/specs/client-engagement-workflow/spec.md\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-27T23:25:10.055Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwzn2lo_ee3ff844ac62":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/engagement-name-note/proposal.md"],"id":"obs_mqwzn2lo_ee3ff844ac62","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"content\":\"---\\nDate: 2026-06-27\\nChange: engagement-name-note\\nRequirements: requirements.md\\n---\\n\\n## Why\\n\\nA client can have more than one business ‚Äî a personal tax return and a corporation, for example ‚Äî but the system currently enforces one engagement per client per tax year, making it impossible to track both filings independently. This change removes that constraint and gives each engag‚Ä¶","sessionId":"10e14017-2f3e-4428-9177-17ccd5eb1fb1","subtitle":"{\"content\":\"---\\nDate: 2026-06-27\\nChange: engagement-name-note\\nRequirements: requirements.md\\n---\\n\\n## Why\\n\\nA clie‚Ä¶","timestamp":"2026-06-27T23:25:31.466Z","title":"Write","type":"file_write"},"obs_mqwzn5jc_e328cdb15767":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwzn5jc_e328cdb15767","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"command\":\"openspec status --change engagement-name-note --json\",\"description\":\"Check status after writing proposal\"} | {\"interrupted\":false,\"isImage\":false,\"noOutputExpected\":false,\"stderr\":\"\",\"stdout\":\"{\\n  \\\"changeName\\\": \\\"engagement-name-note\\\",\\n  \\\"schemaName\\\": \\\"superpowers-driven\\\",\\n  \\\"isComplete\\\": false,\\n  \\\"applyRequires\\\": [\\n    \\\"tasks\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"artifacts\\\": [\\n    {\\n     ‚Ä¶","sessionId":"10e14017-2f3e-4428-9177-17cc